data.description: Huge price reduction!! Built in 2021 with Over 35K in upgrades! Beautiful two-story home in the great Hunters Ranch community. Proximity and easy access to Highway 90, Hwy 211, Potranco Rd and Lackland Air Force Base, schools and shopping centers. This is a 4 bedroom, 3 baths, a big game room and two living rooms with space for an office. This home has many upgrades including quartz countertops, a new island in the kitchen, all tile flooring throughout the first floor, ceiling fans in all rooms, lighting upstairs and more. Don't lose out on this great opportunity. Builder warranties can be transferred. Water Softener does not convey.
